---
// Testimonials Section Component
---

<section id="testimonials" class="bg-[#0F131A] py-24 border-t border-[#2A2F3A]">
	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<div class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Client Feedback</div>
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-gray-100">
				What Founders Say.
			</h2>
		</div>

		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
			<!-- Testimonial 1 -->
			<div class="bg-[#0A0D12] border border-[#2A2F3A] p-8 rounded-2xl">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-1 mb-4">
					<i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
					<i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
					<i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
					<i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
					<i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
				</div>
				<p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
					"Maulana delivered our MVP in exactly 4 weeks. The code quality is exceptional, and we <strong class="text-cyan-400">secured our seed round</strong> thanks to having a working product to show investors."
				</p>
				<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan-900/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
						<i data-lucide="user" class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-400"></i>
					</div>
					<div>
						<div class="font-bold text-gray-200">Sarah Chen</div>
						<div class="text-sm text-gray-500">CEO, HealthTech Startup</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Testimonial 2 -->
			<div class="bg-[#0A0D12] border border-[#2A2F3A] p-8 rounded-2xl">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-1 mb-4">
					<i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
					<i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
					<i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
					<i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
					<i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
				</div>
				<p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
					"After wasting <strong class="text-gray-300">$15k with an agency</strong>, Maulana rebuilt everything in a month. Direct communication, no BS, and the architecture scales beautifully."
				</p>
				<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan-900/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
						<i data-lucide="user" class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-400"></i>
					</div>
					<div>
						<div class="font-bold text-gray-200">Marcus Rodriguez</div>
						<div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Founder, SaaS Platform</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Testimonial 3 -->
			<div class="bg-[#0A0D12] border border-[#2A2F3A] p-8 rounded-2xl">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-1 mb-4">
					<i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
					<i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
					<i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
					<i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
					<i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 fill-yellow-500"></i>
				</div>
				<p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
					"The best investment we made. Our queue management system handles <strong class="text-cyan-400">thousands of users daily</strong>. Maulana's expertise in both frontend and backend is rare."
				</p>
				<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan-900/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
						<i data-lucide="user" class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-400"></i>
					</div>
					<div>
						<div class="font-bold text-gray-200">Dr. Ahmad Fauzi</div>
						<div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Co-founder, Antre.in</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
